{"tid":621535,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「傳換領隊」皇馬想要嘅唔係沙拿......係高普！","createTime":"2018-04-08T11:32:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T11:39:05.000Z","uid":5006,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a299525f414c65b7e577215f455c099605312594","tid":621535,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:32:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/08/192554_0e4839dba3eb904674241ee749b6cc91.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F08%2F192554_0e4839dba3eb904674241ee749b6cc91.png&h=fd342ada&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國《太陽報》大爆，原來皇家馬德里主席皮里茲想要嘅，唔係穆罕默德沙拿，而係利物浦領隊高普，因為佢覺得，現時紅軍嘅進攻足球風格，非常適合皇馬嘅明星陣容，所以正考慮緊搵佢幫手。事實上，之前已經有消息話，假如皇馬唔能夠完成奇迹性嘅歐聯3連霸，就算教練施丹未至於被人炒魷，佢都會冇癮主動離開，就算皮里茲真係睇中高普，都唔係太出奇呀！ <br />\n<br />\n來源：<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180408/mobile/bkn-20180408161005019-0408_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20180408%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180408161005019-0408_00882_001.html&d=gCaSkHP6TFZNESPGO7qoUbZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=e415b0cd\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20180408/mobile/bkn-20180408161005019-0408_00882_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知皇馬盛意禮聘，高普會唔會心郁去教皇馬呢？<br />\n高普都教得利記幾有生氣，就咁走又幾可惜。<br />\n況且，而家班球員都幾撐施丹，就算食雞胸，可能都會比多一季時間？<br />\n大家又覺得高普好啲定施丹好啲？想唔想高普走人替施丹？"},{"pid":"8cadc297c400fca3f9f36284e14124b3303151b0","tid":621535,"uid":47303,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:37:37.000Z","msg":"太陽報"},{"pid":"26c4d8526570aed1841e210652cc86d1a48421c8","tid":621535,"uid":79711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T11:39:05.000Z","msg":"太陽報<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}